data.name: Seer's Eye
metaResult.name: Seer's Eye
metaResult.description:
A single mysterious eyeball suspended in bubbling liquid. It emanates a slowly pulsating pale blue light.
If that effect isn’t unsettling enough, the fact that the eye flicks its gaze about the room of its own volition should do the trick.
metaResult.collection.name: Lordrym's Workshop

data.name: Grim #1547
metaResult.name: Grim #1547
metaResult.description: The Grim Syndicate is a collection of 10,000 generated Grims that do the dirty work of playing afterlife janitors across all planes of existence; in fetching those stubborn Souls who vacate their living vessels but aren’t ready to move on to the Ethereal Realm. What you call a haunting, these Reaper Agents call “all in a day’s work”.
metaResult.collection.name: Grim Syndicate
